<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-834-756  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 834 756.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Lotus  Nov 1989 v5 n11 p114(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Lotus Publishing Corporation 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Analyze buyouts for medium- to small-size businesses.andO;(ValueSource's Buy-Out Plan) (product announcement)andM;</TITLE><DESCRIPT>Company:   ValuSource (product introduction).andO;Product:   Buy-Out Plan (Computer program) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionFinancial Software.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Analyze Buyouts for Medium-to Small-Size Businesses Buy-Out Plan lets youorganize and analyze the complex financial data necessary to evaluate aleveraged buyout or the acquisition of a public or private business worth$100 million or less.andP;  The software lets you analyze the target company'shistorical performance, compare that performance with others in its field,and project its post-sale performance for up to 10 years.andP;  The program alsolets you consider 12 types of funding instruments for a leveraged buyout,including bank notes, revolving loans, and term debt, subordinated debt, andconvertible debt.andP;  And you can consider customized note arrangements withseveral flexible parameters.andP;  You can also assess the impact that retainingthe business's current management or replacing it will have on the company'spost-sale performance.andM;The program includes 13 checks against defaulting on the terms of a loan.andO;You can project income statements, balance sheets, and cash flow statementsover 10 years, as well as project up to 50 new fixed-asset purchases.andO;Built-in inflation tables let you evaluate the effects caused by thefluctuation of prime interest rates, a downturn in the economy, and otherfactors.andP;  A utility, Report Writer, lets you generate a lengthy, writtenfinancial proposal that contains an executive summary, current financialfigures, and graphics.andP;  The written-report file is dynamically linked toworksheet cells for easy report updating.andP;  You can download the report fileinto any of the popular word processor or desktop-publishing packages.andM;Requires 1-2-3 Release 2.01, 2.2, or 3 and at least 640K of RAM.andP;  $690including Report Writer; $195 for Report Writer, from ValueSource, 1939 GrandAve., San Diego, CA 92109; 800-825-8763.andO;</TEXT></DOC>